    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sorry, Wrong Door</strong> is a thrilling online co-op experience for 1-4 players, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >where you and your team are trapped inside a haunted castle. But this is no ordinary castle an all-powerful demon roams its halls, and the only way out is to defeat it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face Terrifying Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133810/extras/2b8d8eda28cfebd7d61992a59a6b5574.poster.avif?t=1771583979\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133810/extras/2b8d8eda28cfebd7d61992a59a6b5574.webm?t=1771583979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133810/extras/2b8d8eda28cfebd7d61992a59a6b5574.mp4?t=1771583979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a procedurally generated nightmare filled with terrifying monsters, cunning traps, and deadly surprises at every turn. Work together, scavenge for weapons, find keys, and fight to survive as the castle constantly shifts around you. The clock is ticking, and the demon is watching.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience Unique Adventures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133810/extras/aa7621edc7b5da1db7a750b70de27c38.poster.avif?t=1771583979\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133810/extras/aa7621edc7b5da1db7a750b70de27c38.webm?t=1771583979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133810/extras/aa7621edc7b5da1db7a750b70de27c38.mp4?t=1771583979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends in intense online co-op mode.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore a castle that changes every time you play, offering endless replayability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Face powerful bosses and claim unique weapon rewards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience pulse pounding moments of horror: from shadowy jump scares to frantic zombie chases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Uncover the mystery, conquer the demon, and escape... or be trapped forever.</p></li></ul>",
